URL: https://github.com/braithwaite/MGRASTer/
Date: 2018-05-07
Description: Convenience functions for using the v.1 API of the
    MG-RAST metagenomics analysis server. <https://api.mg-rast.org>
    This package can construct a model of the API syntax, use the 
    model to validate API calls and API returns, and will place
    low-level requests to the API, automatically managing 
    authorization and returning the data as R frames.  Used by 
    the user-facing client, 'matR', that supports asynchronous 
    requests and metadata download.  MG-RAST is described in 
    Wilke, A. (2013) <10.1016/B978-0-12-407863-5.00022-8> and 
    Meyer, F. (2017) <10.1093/bib/bbx105>.
